137typedef struct
138{
139 union
140 {
141 uint8_t MR0; //Mode register 0
142
143 struct
144 {
145 uint8_t DS : 2; //[0..1] drive strength | 00=50 ohm default, 01=100 ohm, 10=200 ohm, | volatile
146 uint8_t LC : 3; //[2..4] Read latency code. | 010 = RL:3, WL:2, 84MHz | volatile
147 // | 011 = RL:4, WL:3, 104MHz |
148 // | 100 = RL:5, WL:4, 133MHz (default) |
149 // | 101 = RL:6, WL:5, 166MHz |
150 uint8_t BL : 2; //[5..6] Wrapped burst length | 0~3=16B,32B,64B,2KB(default) wrap | volatile
151 uint8_t DM : 1; //[7..7] data mask | 0=ON (default), 1=OFF, | volatile
152 }MR0_b;
153 } ;
154
155}am_devices_mspi_psram_aps12804o_regs_t;
156

604//

606// 1us/64 ~= 15.625ns per step (192MHz clock)
607//
